                <h1>Introduction</h1>
                <p>Learn how to find and complete tasks to earn points and contribute to a greener planet.</p>
                <h1>Types of Tasks</h1>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Recycling tasks:</strong> Tasks that involve recycling materials correctly.</li>
                    <li><strong>Energy-saving tasks:</strong> Activities that help reduce energy consumption.</li>
                    <li><strong>Water conservation tasks:</strong> Initiatives to save water.</li>
                    <li><strong>Community service tasks:</strong> Volunteer activities that benefit the community.</li>
                </ul>
                <h1>How to Find Tasks</h1>
                <p>Tasks are listed in the <a href="/tasks">Tasks</a> section. Use filters or the search bar to find tasks that interest you.</p>
                <h1>Task Details</h1>
                <p>Each task listing includes:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Description:</strong> A summary of what the task involves.</li>
                    <li><strong>Points:</strong> The number of points awarded upon completion.</li>
                    <li><strong>Deadline:</strong> The date by which the task must be completed (if applicable).</li>
                    <li><strong>Steps:</strong> Instructions on how to complete the task.</li>
                </ul>
                <h1>Submitting Completed Tasks</h1>
                <p>To submit a completed task, upload proof (such as photos) through the submission form on the task's page.</p>
                <h1>Earning Points and Rewards</h1>
                <p>Complete tasks to earn points, which can be redeemed for eco-friendly rewards. Track your progress on the <a href="/leaderboard">leaderboard</a>.</p>
